TG %>% 
  filter(supp == "OJ") %>% 
  mutate(effect = len / dose) %>% 
  select(dose, effect) %>% 
  group_by(dose) %>% 
  summarise(mean_eff = mean(effect),
            sd_eff = sd(effect) 
            ) %>% 
  arrange(-mean_eff)

d1 <- 
d0 %>% 
  filter(Matrix %in% c("Mussel", "Oyster")) %>% 
  filter(Parameter %in% c("Zinc", "Zinc - Units in Wet Weight" )) %>% 
  select(Fiscal_Year, Matrix, Scientific_Name, Parameter, Value, Unit)

d1 %>% 
  group_by(Scientific_Name, Matrix) %>% 
  summarise(Number = n(),
            mean = mean(Value),
            sd = sd(Value),
            median = median(Value)
            ) %>% 
  arrange(-median)
